---
title: Orchestration sequence — YAML-driven PipelineInterpreter
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User / UI (React SPA)
    participant API as FastAPI / FastMCP
    participant WM as WorkflowManager
    participant PI as PipelineInterpreter
    participant SE as StepExecutor
    participant DR as derivation_runner
    participant LTM as LTM Repositories
    participant GT as Ground Truth
    participant FS as output_dir (disk)

    U->>API: POST /workflows (spec=adsl_cdiscpilot01.yaml)
    activate API
    API->>WM: start_workflow(spec_path)
    WM->>PI: load pipeline YAML + build FSM
    WM-->>API: workflow_id (202)
    API-->>U: workflow_id
    deactivate API

    Note over PI,SE: parse_spec (builtin)
    PI->>SE: BuiltinStepExecutor.execute
    SE->>FS: write {wf_id}_source.csv (Phase 18.1 snapshot)
    SE-->>PI: ctx.spec + derived_df + synthetic_csv

    Note over PI,SE: build_dag (builtin)
    PI->>SE: BuiltinStepExecutor.execute
    SE-->>PI: ctx.dag (topological layers, one per dependency level)

    Note over PI,DR: derive_variables (parallel_map over DAG layers)
    loop for each layer
        PI->>SE: ParallelMapStepExecutor.execute
        loop for each variable in layer (asyncio.gather)
            SE->>DR: run_variable(variable, ctx, LTMRepos)
            DR->>LTM: query_feedback + query_qc_history + query_patterns
            LTM-->>DR: authority-ranked evidence (human > debugger > prior agent)
            par Coder + QC double programming
                DR->>DR: coder agent (typed I/O)
            and
                DR->>DR: qc agent (isolated context)
            end
            DR->>DR: comparator (row-by-row + AST similarity)
            alt MATCH
                DR->>PI: DAGNode approved (auto)
            else MISMATCH
                DR->>DR: debugger agent
                DR->>PI: DAGNode approved (chose coder or qc)
            end
            DR->>PI: emit CODER_PROPOSED + QC_VERDICT [+ DEBUGGER_RESOLVED] audit events
        end
    end

    Note over PI,GT: ground_truth_check (builtin)
    PI->>SE: BuiltinStepExecutor.execute
    SE->>GT: load reference adsl.xpt + inner-join on USUBJID
    SE->>SE: per-variable compare_results (match/mismatch/total_rows)
    SE-->>PI: ctx.ground_truth_report

    Note over U,PI: human_review (HITL gate)
    PI->>SE: HITLGateStepExecutor.execute
    SE-->>U: status = human_review, awaiting_approval = true
    U->>API: POST /workflows/{id}/approve (per-variable feedback)
    API->>WM: approve_with_feedback_impl
    WM->>LTM: FeedbackRow.save (approved + rejected variables)
    WM-->>SE: release asyncio.Event
    SE-->>PI: emit HUMAN_APPROVED audit event with rich details

    Note over PI,LTM: save_patterns (builtin — LTM write)
    PI->>SE: BuiltinStepExecutor.execute
    SE->>LTM: PatternRepository.store for each approved DAGNode
    SE->>LTM: QCHistoryRepository.store for each coder/qc pair

    Note over PI,SE: audit (agent — auditor)
    PI->>SE: AgentStepExecutor.execute
    SE->>SE: auditor agent → AuditSummary
    SE-->>PI: ctx.audit_trail serialized to JSON

    Note over PI,FS: export (builtin)
    PI->>SE: BuiltinStepExecutor.execute
    SE->>FS: write {wf_id}_adam.csv + {wf_id}_adam.parquet

    PI-->>WM: FSM -> completed
    WM-->>U: status = completed (via polling or MCP notification)
